column1: # Advanced ML Experiment Results Matrix for FigRegistry-Kedro Integration
# This comprehensive experimental dataset demonstrates the sophisticated
# capabilities of the figregistry-kedro plugin integration for automated
# deployment patterns within enterprise data science workflows.
# - Showcase hierarchical condition matching with F-002-RQ-002 wildcard support
# - Demonstrate environment-specific configuration overrides per F-007-RQ-001/002
# - Provide comprehensive statistical data for publication-quality visualizations
# - Enable FigureDataSet parameter injection and context resolution per F-005-RQ-004
# - Support Kedro versioning integration for experiment tracking per F-005-RQ-002
# ✓ Multi-algorithm comparison across baseline/candidate/champion model types
# ✓ Statistical significance testing with p-values and confidence intervals
# ✓ A/B testing framework with treatment groups and control conditions
# ✓ Hyperparameter optimization results with convergence analysis
# ✓ Model interpretability metrics and feature importance rankings
# ✓ Performance monitoring with SLA compliance tracking
# ✓ Publication-ready statistical summaries with effect sizes
# ✓ Enterprise compliance metrics for governance and audit requirements
# - Development: Debug-enabled metrics with verbose diagnostics
# - Staging: Validation-focused metrics with quality gates
# - Production: Performance-optimized metrics with SLA monitoring
# Comma-separated values with comprehensive metadata columns designed to
# trigger sophisticated condition-based styling through FigRegistry's
# hierarchical pattern matching and environment-specific override system.
